@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000
@token = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. JWT Create (Login with Email or Username)
# Base Djoser JWT endpoint
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/jwt/create/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@example.com",
    "password": "1234"
}

### 2. Get My Info (Djoser)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/users/me/
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ0b2tlbl90eXBlIjoiYWNjZXNzIiwiZXhwIjoxNzczNTI1MjE3LCJpYXQiOjE3NzM1MjE2MTcsImp0aSI6ImQzNGJmMWZmMjRiMDRjNzQ4OWI0NDFkOGVhM2I0MGE1IiwidXNlcl9pZCI6IjEifQ.5Ytxufmaj8JZsRjJJeDG8IO7EGGKC5tk4cnEP28mRro

### 3. Create a Course (Instructor Only)
# Note: Ensure category with ID 1 exists first
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/courses/instructor/courses/
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ0b2tlbl90eXBlIjoiYWNjZXNzIiwiZXhwIjoxNzczNDQ2MjM1LCJpYXQiOjE3NzM0NDI2MzUsImp0aSI6ImU3ZjRmYmUxZTUwOTQxNzBhMDJlM2RjMjdjZDg2MDQ5IiwidXNlcl9pZCI6IjEifQ.uoV4om-S1fBukhyvt8UJUI-VF7UhQE0aF3adFZEMoIU
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Django for Beginners",
    "description": "Learn Django from scratch",
    "price": 100.00,
    "category": 1,
    "status": "PUBLISHED"
}

### 4. List All Published Courses
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/courses/public/courses/

### 5. Search Courses by Price
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/courses/public/courses/?price=100

### ---------------------------------------------------------
### Additional Custom V1 Endpoints
### ---------------------------------------------------------

### 6. Login via Custom Identity (Cookies support)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@example.com",
    "password": "1234"
}

### 7. Get Current User Info (Custom V1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/user/
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ0b2tlbl90eXBlIjoiYWNjZXNzIiwiZXhwIjoxNzczNDQ2MjM1LCJpYXQiOjE3NzM0NDI2MzUsImp0aSI6ImU3ZjRmYmUxZTUwOTQxNzBhMDJlM2RjMjdjZDg2MDQ5IiwidXNlcl9pZCI6IjEifQ.uoV4om-S1fBukhyvt8UJUI-VF7UhQE0aF3adFZEMoIU

### 8. Create a Category
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/courses/categories/
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ0b2tlbl90eXBlIjoiYWNjZXNzIiwiZXhwIjoxNzczNDQ2MjM1LCJpYXQiOjE3NzM0NDI2MzUsImp0aSI6ImU3ZjRmYmUxZTUwOTQxNzBhMDJlM2RjMjdjZDg2MDQ5IiwidXNlcl9pZCI6IjEifQ.uoV4om-S1fBukhyvt8UJUI-VF7UhQE0aF3adFZEMoIU
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Programming",
    "icon": "code"
}

### 9. List All Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/courses/categories/

### [1] الحصول على توكن الطالب الأساسي (Student)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/jwt/create/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "new_student@example.com",
    "password": "pass1234"
}

### [2] الحصول على توكن المستخدم الآخر (Other User)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/jwt/create/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "other@example.com",
    "password": "pass1234"
}
### إنشاء حساب جديد (Registration)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/users/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "new_student@example.com",
    "password": "pass1234",
    "re_password": "pass1234",
    "username": "new_user_1"
}

